    public final class TakeLeaseOnLatestItem

    The ICommand for taking a lease on the latest version of an Item.

    Authorization:

    • The current user must have the SecurityAccessLevel.UPDATE access level or the SecurityGrantLevel.UPDATE grant level for the Item being leased.
